dct_description_sm: Relief show by hachures and spot heights. Includes location map. Map shows international, inter-territorial, provincial and distric boundaries, three classes of roads and railways. "D.C.S. 17/34"; "10,500/4/48 S.P.C." Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is attached to companion volume. Map upper right indicates that the map number is "34." Relief show by hachures.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. Directorate of Colonial Surveys
dct_publisher_sm: London : War Office. [General Staff. Geographical Section], 1948.
